[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "[For Many Unknown Little Friends, Including Monica]",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Once upon a time there was a little fat comfortable grey squirrel, called Timmy Tiptoes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "He had a nest thatched with leaves in the top of a tall tree; and he had a little squirrel wife called Goody.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "When Timmy and Goody Tiptoes came to the nut thicket, they found other squirrels were there already.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Timmy took off his jacket and hung it on a twig; they worked away quietly by themselves.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "They carried them away in bags, and stored them in several hollow stumps near the tree where they had built their nest.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "When these stumps were full, they began to empty the bags into a hole high up a tree, that had belonged to a woodpecker; the nuts rattled down-down-down inside.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "\"How shall you ever get them out again?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "It is like a money box!\" said Goody.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "\"I shall be much thinner before springtime, my love,\" said Timmy Tiptoes, peeping into the hole.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "They did collect quantities- because they did not lose them! Squirrels who bury their nuts in the ground lose more than half, because they cannot remember the place.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "The most forgetful squirrel in the wood was called Silvertail.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "He began to dig, and he could not remember.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "And then he dug again and found some nuts that did not belong to him; and there was a fight.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "And other squirrels began to dig,--the whole wood was in commotion!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Unfortunately, just at this time a flock of little birds flew by, from bush to bush, searching for green caterpillars and spiders.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "There were several sorts of little birds, twittering different songs.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Who's been digging up MY nuts?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Who's been digging up MY nuts?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Timmy Tiptoes went on with his work without replying; indeed, the little bird did not expect an answer.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "It was only singing its natural song, and it meant nothing at all.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "The innocent little bird which had caused all the mischief, flew away in a fright!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Timmy rolled over and over, and then turned tail and fled towards his nest, followed by a crowd of squirrels shouting- \"Who's been digging up MY nuts?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "The hole was much too small for Timmy Tiptoes' figure.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000020_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000020_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "\"We will leave him here till he confesses,\" said Silvertail Squirrel and he shouted into the hole-\"Who's been digging up MY nuts?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Timmy Tiptoes made no reply; he had tumbled down inside the tree, upon half a peck of nuts belonging to himself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "He lay quite stunned and still.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Goody Tiptoes picked up the nut bags and went home.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "She made a cup of tea for Timmy; but he didn't come and didn't come.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Goody Tiptoes passed a lonely and unhappy night.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Next morning she ventured back to the nut bushes to look for him; but the other unkind squirrels drove her away.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "She wandered all over the wood, calling-",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "\"Timmy Tiptoes!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000025_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000025_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Oh, where is Timmy Tiptoes?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "In the meantime Timmy Tiptoes came to his senses.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "He found himself tucked up in a little moss bed, very much in the dark, feeling sore; it seemed to be under ground.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000026_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000026_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "There was a chirpy noise, and a small striped Chipmunk appeared with a night light, and hoped he felt better?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "It was most kind to Timmy Tiptoes; it lent him its nightcap; and the house was full of provisions.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "The Chipmunk explained that it had rained nuts through the top of the tree-\"Besides, I found a few buried!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000028_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000028_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "My wife will be anxious!\" \"Just another nut-or two nuts; let me crack them for you,\" said the Chipmunk.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000028_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000028_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Timmy Tiptoes grew fatter and fatter!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Now Goody Tiptoes had set to work again by herself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000029_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000029_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "She did not put any more nuts into the woodpecker's hole, because she had always doubted how they could be got out again.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000029_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000029_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "She hid them under a tree root; they rattled down, down, down.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "My husband, Timmy Tiptoes, has run away too.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "She led the way to the woodpecker's tree, and they listened at the hole.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Down below there was a noise of nutcrackers, and a fat squirrel voice and a thin squirrel voice were singing together-",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "\"My little old man and I fell out, How shall we bring this matter about? Bring it about as well as you can, And get you gone, you little old man!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "\"You could squeeze in, through that little round hole,\" said Goody Tiptoes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "\"Yes, I could,\" said the Chipmunk, \"but my husband, Chippy Hackee, bites!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Down below there was a noise of cracking nuts and nibbling; and then the fat squirrel voice and the thin squirrel voice sang-",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Then Goody peeped in at the hole, and called down-\"Timmy Tiptoes!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Oh fie, Timmy Tiptoes!\" And Timmy replied, \"Is that you, Goody Tiptoes?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000038_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000038_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Why, certainly!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "He came up and kissed Goody through the hole; but he was so fat that he could not get out.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "And so it went on for a fort night; till a big wind blew off the top of the tree, and opened up the hole and let in the rain.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Then Timmy Tiptoes came out, and went home with an umbrella.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "But Chippy Hackee continued to camp out for another week, although it was uncomfortable.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000044_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000044_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "At last a large bear came walking through the wood. Perhaps he also was looking for nuts; he seemed to be sniffing around.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "Chippy Hackee went home in a hurry!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "And when Chippy Hackee got home, he found he had caught a cold in his head; and he was more uncomfortable still.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000047_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000047_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "And now Timmy and Goody Tiptoes keep their nut store fastened up with a little padlock.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-569_126489_000048_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/569/126489/569_126489_000048_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-569",
        "content": "And whenever that little bird sees the Chipmunks, he sings-\"Who's been digging up MY nuts?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    }
]